{"tid":58070,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"天啊！以色列女兵都超正　清涼辣照被瘋傳","createTime":"2016-12-28T13:58:00.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-28T15:33:41.000Z","uid":19707,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3901c1e65c083176be445f46ddfeae5abe880aa0","tid":58070,"uid":19707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:58:00.000Z","msg":"女大兵的形象可以是嚴肅地保衛國家，但以色列女大兵的生活照可能會顛覆平常人的思考，因為她們不吝於秀出自己的清涼超辣身材，讓世界網友看到，原來以色列女大兵的正妹超多。<br />\n <br />\n據英國《每日郵報》報導，以色列規定國民年滿18歲，無論男女，人人都要服兵役，為期2年。而在Instagram的一個帳號「超辣以色列女大兵(The Hot Israeli Army Girls)」，就貼出各個女生在軍旅生活之外，也有美麗自信的一面。她們除了穿著軍裝、配槍，也會到海灘穿著清涼比基尼，展示好身材。據悉該帳號已有超過34500位追隨者，收錄超過2000位女大兵美姿。<br />\n <br />\n台灣網友紛紛表示：「以色列女兵都殺晒全台男媽寶兵。」、「追不到，語言不通。」、「戰力真強大。」、「男女平等在這。」、「還減肥上健身房幹嘛，去當兵就好啦。」、「以色列招募傭兵嗎？」（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20161228/1022281\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20161228%2F1022281&d=pEmv80Ww3uRh8MVoZrTHP0sIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=9644a547\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20161228/1022281</a><br />\n<br />\nPhoto later"},{"pid":"f2b93ce4cf4cf83b750ac6c747183e165e56ceb2","tid":58070,"uid":19707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T13:59:44.000Z","msg":"Ig:hotisraeliarmygirls"},{"pid":"b1630eb100c76f541a9ed2de21cd5c9cf97a3efc","tid":58070,"uid":19707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T14:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fda1022b4f45096ed092a1f7a4c81ab777d74f7b","tid":58070,"uid":15154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-28T14:53:50.000Z","msg":"Wonder woman <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09840e669f9628ca22390bf92370021360c3a6d6","tid":58070,"uid"